---
title: tags 标签模块丢失问题
date: 2022-12-4 22:47:54
tags: 环境搭建
---

##### 1.在 blog 根目录下执行：
npm i hexo-generator-json-content --save

这一步如果报错：
npm ERR! path /Users/shirley/workspace/blog/node_modules/_anymatch@3.1.3@anymatch/node_modules/picomatch
npm ERR! code ENOENT
npm ERR! errno -2
npm ERR! syscall access
npm ERR! enoent ENOENT: no such file or directory, access '/Users/shirley/workspace/blog/node_modules/_anymatch@3.1.3@anymatch/node_modules/picomatch'
npm ERR! enoent This is related to npm not being able to find a file.
npm ERR! enoent 

npm ERR! A complete log of this run can be found in:
npm ERR!     /Users/shirley/.npm/_logs/2022-12-04T14_38_59_299Z-debug.log

先执行：
 rm -rf node_modules && npm install --force
再执行：
 npm i hexo-generator-json-content --save

##### 2.在博客配置文件 _config.yml 配置：
jsonContent:
    meta: false
    pages: false
    posts:
      title: true
      date: true
      path: true
      text: false
      raw: false
      content: false
      slug: false
      updated: false
      comments: false
      link: false
      permalink: false
      excerpt: false
      categories: false
      tags: true

